I'm sorry, there's nothing I can do.
\lyonI'll help you find her!\.\. Do you know what she looks like?
\lspi[150]\n<Happy Girl>She has long brown hair,\. and a white thingy on her head!
\lyonI see\..\..\.. Well,\. follow me.\.\.\. Let's find her!
